# Butterfly Demo

Follow the instructions below to run the applications successfully

- Both applications are build as workspace and configured with
  Lerna

> ğŸ’¡ for more information check the [documentation](https://lerna.js.org/docs/getting-started)

    npm install

- Once the above command is executed, configure the database for that
  there is a docker-compose with all the necessary configuration

>

    docker compose up -d

- Populate the database so that it has questions already set randomly

  >

      npm run db:seeds

- Finally you run the applications in a single command

>

    npm run dev

> Note: Check the package.json file in the differents workspace to see
> more details.

There are some tests for the backend, to run them run

    npm run test
